  "text": "🎙️ Building a Platform That Helps 60 Teams Work Better — Live Tonight!\n\nTonight at 6 PM, I’ll be joining Petr Polak and Roman Provazník on PodVocasem LIVE to talk about what it takes to build a process and application platform in a large organization, how to improve the work of 60 teams at once, and about DevOps and software development along the way.\n\nYou’ll also hear from Michal Benatsky and Honza Javorek, who will bring fresh perspectives on junior developers, Python, AI, and even game engines — so there’s plenty to look forward to!\n\n📌Join us in person at Bistro-B (Budějovická)\n👉 Register here: www.podvocasem.cz/live",
